  "comment": "Atomic Pro Probeam 8R: The Atomic Pro Probeam 8R, in this kit version including two fixtures and a flight case, is a powerful multifunctional moving head with a 250W OSRAM lamp. It has all the features that make it suitable for a wide variety of situations: automatic, cascading with master/slave, and DMX protocol with assignable channels directly from the convenient control panel with monochrome display and keypad.",
